$Id: README,v 2.1 2007/01/30 04:14:03 comdog Exp $

This is a module Bundle, meaning that it merely lists modules
to install. CPAN.pm handles this just fine.

	perl -MCPAN -e 'install Bundle::MasteringPerl'

After installing this bundle, you should have all of the modules
necessary to play with any of the code in Mastering Perl:

	http://www.oreilly.com/catalog/9780596527242/
	http://www.pair.com/comdog/mastering_perl

Enjoy, 

brian d foy, bdfoy@cpan.org